==Korean==
===Noun===
'''요람''' ([[搖籃]], ''yoram'')
#[[cradle]] (''from Old English [[cradol]] "[[basket]]"'')  cf. Latin '''[[cunae]]'''
#* '''요람'''에서 [[무덤]]까지 (''yoram-eseo mudeom-kkaji'') [[lifetime]], from the [[cradle]] to the [[grave]], from [[birth]] to [[death]], from [[womb]] to [[tomb]]
#[[cradleland]]  (''place of origin'')

====Derived terms====
*요람[[기]] (-[[期]], ''-gi'')  [[infancy]] (''age or stage of origin'') 
*요람[[지]] (-[[地]], ''-ji'')  [[cradleland]] (''place of origin'')

====Related terms====
* 요 ([[搖]], ''yo'')  [[rock]]ing, [[roll]]ing, [[swing]]ing cf. Greek [[κούνια]] (kunia) "[[swing]]"
* 람 ([[籃]], ''ram'') [[basket]] cf. Old English [[cradol]] "[[basket]]"

