*[[그네]] (''geune'') [[swing]] cf. Greek [[κούνια]] ('''kunia''') "[[swing]]", Latin '''[[cunae]]''' "[[cradle]]"
*[[바구니]] (''baguni'') [[basket]]
*[[흔들다]] (''heundeulda'') To [[rock]], [[roll]]
*[[건들거리다]] (''geondeul-georida'') To [[rock]], [[roll]], [[swing]] (''repeatedly'') cf. '''[[gondola]]''', Italian [[dondolare]] (''probably, frequentative'') 

